Well, yes - father was always served first. We all sat round the table, yes, I remember sitting in the - high chair there - then, and we were all served one after the other, the eldest first and then the - father first and then the - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5178298 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1707796\charrsid675430 William first?
