e and this gong, and these swing doors, from the kitchen, leading from the kitchen department into the - hall, and I could hear her playing and I just opened these - listened. And she came out - and caught me. She said, what are you doing there? I said - 
I
 was listening to you playing. That's nothing to do with you, you go into your own place. That's very rude. But she did - she used to play that - Humoresque used - I used to like best. And - American - the American - anthem. She'd play that. Yes. Yes. The
y play that now.
