ed to - she'd ring this - bell. She used to have a little bell, not the gong. And we'd all march into the - breakfast room as we called it there. And we'd each have a chair to kneel at. Say these prayers. Read a verse out of the Bible or a chapter and - s
ay these few prayers and then - we'd have to go out again.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5178298 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1707796\charrsid675430 So you all went in?
